reviewText: This movie is really a line of episodes(I estimate 6-10,some thing similair),a line of great episodes! This movies is fun to watch and is defintly NOT boring! If you are an adult who liked gumby as a child,you will love this movie! This movie is great for kids and adults! Plus Gumby(shows and movies) is something that you want worry about because it has no violence! Now the show of Gumby is on Cartoon Network and is a perfect place for this show. I would say that Gumby is not on to watch enough though. This movie is well worth the money.
